Package: architekter
Title: Build a {ggplot} Maquette from Figma File
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Margot", "Brard", , "margot@thinkr.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6754-0659")),
    person("ThinkR", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Use a Figma file -a free online UI/UX design tool- to build a
    theme for your graphics created with {ggplot2}. Create a theme,
    palettes and scale functions easily.
